    public class ArjFileSet
extends CommonsCompressFileSet
    A ArjFileSet is a FileSet with extra attributes useful in the context of Arj tasks. A ArjFileSet extends FileSets with the ability to extract a subset of the entries of a Arj file for inclusion in another Arj file. It also includes a prefix attribute which is prepended to each entry in the output Arj file.
    Since:
    Apache Compress Antlib 1.3
